'''''How To Be A Fan With Hex''''' is an Australian [[observational documentary]] [[web series]] created and presented by [[Stephanie Bendixsen]]. The show originally aired on [[ABC iview]] on September 5, 2016.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://iview.abc.net.au/collection/hex |title=How To Be A Fan With Hex: Complete Series : ABC iview |website=Iview.abc.net.au |date=2016-09-05 |accessdate=2017-01-13}}</ref> This web series' goal is to explore fandoms of different [[popular culture|pop culture]] branches, and to figure out exactly what drives individuals to participate in these groups, through Bendixsen's interviews and engagement in the activities.

